items.htmlTitle: Bruun's FFT algorithm - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
Bruun's algorithm is a fast Fourier transform (FFT) algorithm based on an unusual 
recursive polynomial-factorization approach, proposed for powers of two by G.
